Experiencing the same issue. It appears that `appState.collaborators` is being serialized as an object instead of an array.

**Edit:** Ah, it's because `appState.collaborators` is a `Map`, so if you call `JSON.stringify`, it gets serialized as a plain object.

@Mounir-abaddah you can likely solve your issue by manually overwriting `appState.collaborators`, but there must be a better fix to this...
```
